organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Epiphanny Prince scored 18 of her 27 points in the second half to boost Rutgers to a surprisingly lopsided victory over Auburn, which had won its first 20 games and was ranked in the top 10.
